gpt_zero_shot.prompt: give me the total articles per journal
gpt_zero_shot.sql_query:
SELECT journal AS journal_name, COUNT(DISTINCT article_id) AS total_articles
FROM papers
GROUP BY journal
ORDER BY journal_name
